@startuml
title Ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe - Project Structure and Flow
allowmixing
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho

package "uttt/game" {
  class UltimateTicTacToeGame {
    +board_rep: ndarray(9x9)
    +full_board: ndarray(3x3x3x3)
    +sub_boards: ndarray(3x3)
    +empty_places: list[set[cell]]
    +empty_sub_places: set[subboard]
    +curr_board: tuple | None
    +q_table: LMDBQTable | dict
    +gamma: float
    --
    +init_game()
    +legal_moves()
    +apply_move(bi,bj,r,c,symbol)
    +find_smart_move_candidates(...)
    +best_from_moves(moves)
    +all_symmetries_fast(board)
    +canonical_board_int(board)
    +play_one_game(...)
    +current_board_value()
  }

  class LMDBQTable {
    +path: str
    +env: lmdb.Environment
    --
    +begin_read()
    +get(state_int)
    +__setitem__(state_int, value)
    +iter_entries()
    +update_from_targets(board_score_list)
    +batch_merge_local_q(local_q)
  }

  class Games {
    +num_games: int
    +processes: int
    +chunk_size: int
    +agent_wins: int
    +player_wins: int
    +ties: int
    --
    +multi_process_train()
    +single_process_train(...)
  }

  class "hashing.py <<module>>" as Hashing {
    +encode_board_to_int(board)
    +decode_board_from_int(value)
  }
}

package "uttt/data_build" {
  class "build_filtered_db.py <<module>>" as BuildFiltered {
    +main()
  }

  class "build_mixed_db.py <<module>>" as BuildMixed {
    +states_needed(...)
    +compute_target_state_counts(...)
    +classify_bucket(...)
    +sample_lmdb_states(...)
    +write_lmdb_rows(...)
    +main()
  }

  class ReservoirStates {
    +capacity: int
    +items: list
    +seen: int
    --
    +add(item)
  }
}

package "uttt/ml" {
  class ModelD {
    +mb: Sequential
    +fc: Sequential
    --
    +forward(x)
  }

  class NpyDataset {
    +X: ndarray
    +y: ndarray
    --
    +__len__()
    +__getitem__(idx)
  }

  class "cnn_core.py <<module>>" as CnnCore {
    +pick_device()
    +build_model(option)
    +load_trained_model(option)
    +build_npy_dataloaders(...)
    +evaluate_mse(...)
    +train_supervised_model(...)
  }

  class UltimateTicTacToeCNN {
    +model: nn.Module
    +device: torch.device
    +mode: str
    --
    +board_to_tensor(board)
    +value_of_board(board)
    +best_from_moves(moves)
    +agent_smart_move()
    +current_board_value()
  }
}

package "uttt/ui" {
  class BoardGrid {
    +game: UltimateTicTacToeGame
    +buttons: list[list[CellButton]]
    +status_label
    +app
    --
    +on_cell_pressed(btn)
    +refresh()
    +show_result()
    +update_grid_lines()
  }

  class UTTTApp {
    +opponent_type: str
    +cnn_option: str
    +game
    +board_grid
    --
    +build()
    +build_intro_screen()
    +build_game_screen()
    +init_game_instance()
    +activate_game_board()
    +update_value_label()
    +play_ai_turn()
  }

  class "api.py <<module>>" as ApiModule {
    +legal_global_moves(game)
    +build_prompt(game, legal_moves)
    +extract_move(text)
    +get_ai_move(game)
  }
}

package "artifacts and files" {
  database "fixed_qtable.lmdb" as FixedQtable
  file "filtered_X.npy\nfiltered_y.npy" as FilteredNpy
  file "mixed_X.npy\nmixed_y.npy" as MixedNpy
  file "model_*.pt\nbest_model_*.pt" as ModelFiles
}

UltimateTicTacToeCNN --|> UltimateTicTacToeGame

Games --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : runs repeated self-play
UltimateTicTacToeGame --> LMDBQTable : reads/writes state values
LMDBQTable --> Hashing : state_int <-> board
LMDBQTable --> FixedQtable : stores canonical states

BuildFiltered --> LMDBQTable : scans entries
BuildFiltered --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : expands symmetries
BuildFiltered --> FilteredNpy : writes filtered dataset

BuildMixed --> LMDBQTable : samples visits==1 states
BuildMixed --> ReservoirStates : bucket sampling
BuildMixed --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : decode + symmetries
BuildMixed --> FilteredNpy : reads base rows
BuildMixed --> MixedNpy : writes mixed dataset

CnnCore --> NpyDataset : loads numpy boards
CnnCore --> ModelD : representative default model
CnnCore --> MixedNpy : trains from mixed dataset
CnnCore --> ModelFiles : saves checkpoints and best model

UltimateTicTacToeCNN --> CnnCore : load trained model
UltimateTicTacToeCNN --> ModelFiles : uses checkpoint at inference

UTTTApp --> BoardGrid : owns and refreshes board view
UTTTApp --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : Q-table / API modes
UTTTApp --> UltimateTicTacToeCNN : CNN mode
UTTTApp --> ApiModule : API mode only
BoardGrid --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : apply_move(), legal_moves(), current_board_value()
ApiModule --> UltimateTicTacToeGame : reads legal moves and board state

note right of Games
Flow step 1:
Runs many episodes and calls
play_one_game() repeatedly.
end note

note right of LMDBQTable
Flow step 2:
Persists canonical board states
with averaged q_value and visits.
end note

note right of BuildMixed
Flow step 3:
Turns LMDB knowledge into
balanced supervised datasets.
end note

note right of CnnCore
Flow step 4:
Builds dataloaders, trains CNN,
evaluates MSE, and saves checkpoints.
end note

note right of UltimateTicTacToeCNN
Flow step 5:
Scores each legal move and
chooses the highest-value board.
end note

note right of UTTTApp
Flow step 6:
Exposes the chosen agent through GUI
and coordinates human/AI turns.
end note

@enduml
